<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>CONFIDENTIAL ASSESMENTS</title>
    <link
      href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css"
      rel="stylesheet"
      integrity="sha384-QWTKZyjpPEjISv5WaRU9OFeRpok6YctnYmDr5pNlyT2bRjXh0JMhjY6hW+ALEwIH"
      crossorigin="anonymous"
    />
    <style>
      body {
        margin: 0;
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        background-color: #73ccd0;
      }
      header {
        font-size: larger;
        font-weight: 800;
        background-color: white;
      }
      form {
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        background-color: #fee252;
        padding: 30px;
        border-radius: 10px;
        box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
      }

      label {
        font-weight: bold;
        margin-bottom: 10px;
        display: block;
        color: #333;
      }

      input[type="date"],
      input[type="time"],
      input[type="text"] {
        width: 100%;
        padding: 12px;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
        border: none;
        border-radius: 8px;
        background-color: #f1ef99;
        box-shadow: inset 0 0 5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
      }

      input[type="date"]:focus,
      input[type="time"]:focus,
      input[type="text"]:focus {
        background-color: #f1ef99;
      }

      input[type="submit"] {
        background-color: #f1ef99;
        color: black;
        border: none;
        padding: 15px 20px;
        cursor: pointer;
        border-radius: 8px;
        transition: background-color 0.3s;
      }

      input[type="submit"]:hover {
        background-color: #45a049;
      }
      .qn {
        padding-bottom: 30px;
      }
      .writeup h1,
      .qn h1 {
        color: white;
        text-shadow: 2px 2px #111;
      }
      .lead {
        font-weight: 600;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <header>
      <div class="container">
        <header
          class="d-flex flex-wrap align-items-center justify-content-center justify-content-md-between py-3 mb-4 border-bottom"
        >
          <div class="col-md-1 mb-2 mb-md-0">
            <a
              href="/"
              class="d-inline-flex link-body-emphasis text-decoration-none"
            >
              <img
                src="/Images/logo-for-mental-health-include-compass (1).jpeg"
                width="50"
              />
            </a>
          </div>
          <ul
            class="nav col-12 col-md-auto mb-2 justify-content-center mb-md-0"
          >
            <li>
              <a href="home" class="nav-link px-2" style="color: #111">HOME</a>
            </li>
            <li>
              <a href="assessments" class="nav-link px-2" style="color: #111"
                >ASSESSMENTS</a
              >
            </li>
            <li>
              <a href="therapy" class="nav-link px-2" style="color: #111"
                >THERAPY</a
              >
            </li>
            <li>
              <a href="community" class="nav-link px-2" style="color: #111"
                >COMMUNITY CONNECT</a
              >
            </li>
            <li>
              <a href="resource" class="nav-link px-2" style="color: #111"
                >RESOURCES</a
              >
            </li>
          </ul>
          <div class="col-md-1 text-end">
            <a href="profile"><img src="/Images/user.gif" width="70" /></a>
          </div>
        </header>
      </div>
    </header>
    <div class="container">
      <section class="writeup">
        <div class="container col-xxl-12 px-4 py-5">
          <div class="row flex-lg-row-reverse align-items-center g-5 py-5">
            <div class="col-10 col-sm-8 col-lg-6">
              <img
                src="/Images/mental-health-illustration_634548677.jpg"
                class="d-block mx-lg-auto img-fluid"
                alt="Bootstrap Themes"
                width="700"
                height="500"
                loading="lazy"
              />
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-6">
              <h1 class="display-5 fw-bold lh-1 mb-3">
                Confidential Assessments
              </h1>
              <p class="lead">
                Embarking on a journey towards improved mental well-being begins
                with understanding where you currently stand. At Inner Compass,
                we offer confidential assessments designed to provide insight
                into your mental health and help you chart a path towards
                greater wellness. Our assessments are carefully crafted to
                respect your privacy and confidentiality while providing
                valuable insights that can guide you on your journey. Whether
                you're exploring therapy options, seeking to understand your
                current mental state, or simply curious about areas for
                potential growth, our assessments are here to support you every
                step of the way. Take the first step towards a brighter future
                by embarking on a confidential assessment journey with Inner
                Compass today.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>
      <section class="qn">
        <h1 class="display-5 fw-bold lh-1 mb-3">Daily Review</h1>
        <p class="lead">
          Embark on your journey to self-discovery and well-being! Dive into our
          assessment and uncover insights to guide your journey.
        </p>
        <form method="post" action="/assesments">
          <label for="q2"
            >1.Hold on is it still Sunday or am I dreaming? What's the day
            today?</label
          ><br />
          <input type="text" placeholder="Monday" id="q2" name="day" /><br />

          <label for="q3"
            >2.Time to test your temporal prowess! Can you tell me what time it
            is? Tick-tock, make your guess!</label
          ><br />
          <input type="text" placeholder="Morning" id="q3" name="time" /><br />

          <label for="q4">3.What would you like to do today? </label><br />
          <input
            type="text"
            placeholder="Activities"
            id="q4"
            name="activity"
          /><br />

          <label for="q5"
            >4.Imagine a vast library of information, constantly buzzing with
            potential for discovery. That's kind of how I feel-energized by the
            chance to learn and create something new with every interaction. How
            are you feeling today? </label
          ><br />
          <input type="text" placeholder="Mood " id="q5" name="mood" />
          <input type="submit" value="Submit" />
        </form>
      </section>
    </div>
    <footer style="background-color: white">
      <div class="container">
        <footer
          class="row row-cols-1 row-cols-sm-2 row-cols-md-5 py-5 my-5 border-top"
